	<h1 class="title">2 万块乐高积木变成艺术品之后，就是这样的</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/37534/small/37534.JPG?1421809836" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">石玉 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-26 13:10:37 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16576/medium/16576.png?1445829499" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


